com.badlogic.gdx.automation.recorder

Interface InputValue.SyncValueVisitor

  • Enclosing class:
    InputValue

    public static interface InputValue.SyncValueVisitor
    An interface to enable the visitor pattern on InputValue.SyncValues. This means, it helps to have the JVM do the dispatching of the concrete underlying InputValue.SyncValue type of an instance. Using this interface also adds compiler support for adding new types, since extending the interface automatically breaks concrete implementations that are not adapted for the newly added types.
